hi, i am trying to do the event test and its not working
Hi there! Let's get this sorted out. Could you please let me know which tracking platform you're using for the event test? This will help me provide more specific guidance.
i mean the test pixel integration step that you guys require to run ads

Got it! To test your pixel integration, make sure you've followed these steps:

1. Log in to your Ad Manager account and go to Tools > Event Management.
2. Click on 'Create/Test web event' and set up your event.
3. Use the 'Go test' feature at the bottom of the page to ensure that the test result is successful.

If you're still having trouble, please check if the tracking platform is recording the click. If it is but not showing a conversion, verify with your offer provider if the event constitutes a conversion.

For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this [Event Tracking guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/23053537846669-Introduction-to-Multi-Event-Tracking). Let me know if you need further assistance!
id like to speak with a human
I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
ive already done all of that

Thanks for letting me know. If you've already completed the steps and are still facing issues, I recommend reaching out to our support team for more detailed assistance. You can email them at adsupport@newsbreak.com with your account details and a description of the issue. They'll be able to provide more specific help.
